title: ** 3 BED / 1 BATH ** J/Z/C trains!
posting_body: ["Half month's broker fee", 'September 1st move in date', 'Lovely Sunlit 3 Bedroom!', '*Exposed Brick Living Room with window* Tons of sunlight!', 'Located in Cypress Hills Brooklyn.', 'Just a few blocks from J and Z trains at Alabama Avenue for easy commute into Bushwick and Williamsburg.', 'Quiet Neigborhood also near A and C express trains at Liberty Avenue.', 'A refreshing Apartment with an open exposed brick living room open to the kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances, a granite countertop, and big window flooding the room with light!', 'Tall ceilings add to the spaciousness.', 'Nice sized bedrooms and windows!!', 'Full sized modern bathroom with deep tub and shower Central Heating Only - You will need window units for air conditioning Guarantors accepted Central Heat Exposed Brick large living room with windows Pets Allowed *', 'Upon approval Stainless Steel Appliances Granite Countertop High Ceilings Showing by appointment only - Broker fee in the amount of half months rent is due at signing']
